org.apache.flex.swc

Interface ISWCManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SWCManager

    public interface ISWCManager
    ISWCManager is a repository of SWC library models. It has all the SWC libraries shared within a workspace.

    • Method Detail

      • get

        ISWC get(File file)
        Get the SWC model of the given SWC file. If the manager has a valid model for the file, it returns it. Otherwise, it will parse the SWC file, store the model and return it.
        Parameters:
        file - SWC file
        Returns:
        SWC model
